 OOC: Tyrael should know who Blackheart is he is a famous tripred general on 
cybertron, and in the storyline I had magnus create hes been waging a war on 
cybertorn with the back of the tripred council..and he has won..with a very 
special guest.


Ultra Magnus pressed down on the comm button. He screamed into it "Rodimus, 
Kup Blackheart is coming you must get here now! Kup you know who he is 
bringing with him! Its the worst I could possibly fear. He then implanted a 
codded message that only kup would undertand.."It also means that our tripred 
friends wont be friends much longer once they find out what only his coming 
can mean...the tripreds have won cybertron!"
